msg: - Hardcode UIComponent and Converter types in the plugin for now
- Fix the type of "binding" in the Trinidad metadata to be UIComponent
ADFFACES-476: add a <disableIdExpressions> configuration hook for turning off
- Also update the Trinidad component generation to use getExpressionString() instead of
getValue(null), thereby bypassing coercion, for all types where Strings are processed
- And update the MyFaces component generation similarly, though just for converter
- Add <coerceStrings> configuration hook for forcing java.lang.String coercion where
absolutely necessary - it may be necessary to turn this on at a per-property level
